    <item>
      <title>virtualbox虚机互通配置</title>
      <link>https://test692618.github.io/post/%E6%9D%82%E9%A1%B9/virtualbox%E8%99%9A%E6%9C%BA%E4%BA%92%E9%80%9A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:40:44 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (L)</author>
      <guid>https://test692618.github.io/post/%E6%9D%82%E9%A1%B9/virtualbox%E8%99%9A%E6%9C%BA%E4%BA%92%E9%80%9A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>virtualbox虚机互通配置</h1><p>作者：L（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <p>使用以下命令创建内部网络和DHCP服务器</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">VBoxManage dhcpserver add --netname fylab --ip 10.10.10.1 --netmask 255.255.255.0 --lowerip 10.10.10.2 --upperip 10.10.10.212 --enable 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">netname，网络的名称，这里指定一个叫fylab,你可以随便取
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ip，该DHCP的静态IP地址，也是网关的IP
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">netmask，该网络的子网掩码
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">lowerip代表是该DHCP服务器可以分配的ip的最小ip
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">upperip代表是该DHCP服务器可以分配的ip的最大ip
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">大家都知道DHCP服务器是用来动态分配IP地址的，lowerip和upperip两个参数就规定了DHCP可以分配的IP地址范围
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>选择内部网络模式，并更改名称，即可组件虚拟局域网。</p>
<p><img src="./../../images/image-20240221200813709.png" alt="image-20240221200813709"></p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2024-02-21首发于<a href='https://test692618.github.io/'>HELLO WORLD</a>，最后修改于2024-02-21</p>]]>
      </description>
      
